<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. A bei sawt ngei ie maw,
 I khawvel damlai niteu haw hih
 Kipahna pak chul kit ding ei tau,
 I kikhenna ding un,
 Kawla nisa a hungsuok kittai,
 Kikhen lohna gam ngaih a um ngei ie,

[V2]
 Kikhen lohna mi gen gam nuom achun,
 Len-guol ngaih kimin chawl hitiu;
 Ei vengpa Lal Krista,
 I Hukdampau deihum keng bulah,
 Lungkhamna bei tana.

[V3]
 2. Khawvela hin chu Aw,
 Kap leh mauin alang vai mah leh
 Buoina khela khun gam hawih a um,
 I Hukdampau Krista,
 Zuia I hinnau I phal uchun,
 Zie gamhawih achun naubang nui hitiu.

[V4]
 3. Nawpna pak lunna mun,
 Hukdampa Krista lenna mun chu,
 Ngaiin nichengin ka gal thila,
 Van Angel vamte leh-
 Guol deih gibang i khensau haw tawh,
 Bangtik leh nunnuom in i kikhawm dem?

[V5]
 4. I len-guol ngaih cheng tawh,
 I Pau nasem hitiu kipakin,
 Hun hi nicheng a liemzing ie,
 Zingsawl Aksi vak hawih,
 A hung latna ding phat a nai tai,
 Nasep zoa i chawlhna ding niu chu.

[V6]
 5. Aw, ka Lal Hukdampa,
 Ka kipahnau pakin hung lunin;
 Khawvel nawpna pak atuoi-zo ie,
 Na mel a hin chu aw-
 Kipahna tincheng a lang khawm hi,
 Kipahna pak Saron pak hawih-Na hi.</lyrics>
<title>Kikhen Lohna Gam</title>
<hymn_number>299</hymn_number>
<author>Thangngur</author>
</song>